parameters: Kru: "I'm always causing you trouble, aren't I..."
Maid: "No, not at all. I'm well compensated..."
Ah... that's right... this is how I've been living...
The maid prepares meals like this for me...
Then before sleeping, I reminisce about the past...
Thinking of Umi... and falling asleep...
Have I been living like this all along...?
Having a good job... indeed... it was a luxurious environment for me...
Sigh... what's been going on since a while ago...
What the... who is this child...
Mia: "Geez! Daddy! Are you even listening?"
Mia: "Huh? Daddy!... Why are you crying?"
What's going on... I can't keep up...
Mia: "Did someone bully you? Alright! Mia will teach them a lesson!"
Mia: "Then we need to get Mommy to comfort you..."
Mia: "Yes! If Mommy pats you, you'll cheer up right away!"
Kru: "Mommy as in... could it be..."

Maid: "Oh, Kru dear... Have you forgotten about Miss Umi? You're going to
get scolded～"
Maid: "Miss Umi went shopping just a moment ago."
Kru: "Ah... um... please take care of this child... Mia!"
Kru: "I'll be back soon, so just wait a little!"
